As he had been on steroids for two-months back in July of last year, I have communicated with the primary service he will need a stress steroid prep.  He has been cleared by Cardiology and has had no other significant cardiac symptoms.  Since he was cleared a few months ago, I feel he is an acceptable candidate to undergo the proposed procedure.  I recommend restarting his Plavix as soon as it is reasonable postoperatively.
